0.007   2019-10-24  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- [Deprecation] list_git_release_tags(): rename 'regex' argument to
          'release_tag_regex'. Old argument name still supported for now but
          deprecated & undocumented and will be removed in the future.

	- list_git_release_tags(): return author_name & author_email
	  fields, add options author_name_regex & author_email_regex to
	  filter certain tags only.


0.006   2019-10-24  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- [refactor] Refactor release tags pattern to Regexp-Pattern-Git.

        - [bugfix] Updated release tags pattern was not used.


0.005   2019-10-24  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- [ux] Expand default regex to include e.g. rel-1.23, release1.23,
	  as well as (version,ver,v)-1.23 (separated by dash/underscore).


